<li><i><a href="/wiki/Ultra_vires" title="Ultra vires">Ultra vires</a></i></li></ul></td>
</tr><tr><th class="sidebar-heading">
Grounds for <a href="/wiki/Judicial_review" title="Judicial review">judicial review</a></th></tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Fettering_of_discretion_in_Singapore_administrative_law" title="Fettering of discretion in Singapore administrative law">Fettering of discretion</a></li>
